(communication reliability is stable. Second, role comfort and team trust are co-dependent,) Tj
T*
(especially for high-variance duelists. Third, emotional regulation is not a soft extra but a) Tj
T*
(direct performance variable in long series. Phantom Signal's turnaround is therefore less a) Tj
